Reflection
This activity helped me understand that bias in AI is not always obvious or harmful. In some cases, AI systems attempt to reduce bias by providing neutral responses, but this can result in overly general answers. It reinforced the importance of critically evaluating AI-generated content and recognising both bias and bias mitigation
